Run your hands over the cards.

214
00:19:55,089 --> 00:19:56,590
我媽媽畫過這些
My mom painted these.

215
00:19:56,674 --> 00:19:58,342
是的，你媽媽送的
Yes. They were a gift.

216
00:19:59,719 --> 00:20:02,388
看看你拿到哪一張牌
Let's see which card gets picked.

217
