What the hell?

238
00:22:13,018 --> 00:22:14,478
你嚇到我了
You scared me.

239
00:22:14,562 --> 00:22:16,689
這究竟發生過什麼？
What the hell happened here?

240
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:19,525
- 我媽媽不見了  - 什麼？
- My mom's missing. - What?

241
00:22:19,608 --> 00:22:22,444
