Okay, now I can't see him, either.

247
00:22:40,629 --> 00:22:42,715
傑斯·維蘭德，邪靈獵手
Jace Wayland, demon hunter.

248
00:22:45,467 --> 00:22:47,845
西蒙·盧易斯，解鎖師
Simon Lewis, Keymaster.

249
00:22:47,928 --> 00:22:48,975
你是門衛嗎？
Are you the Gatekeeper?

250
00:22:48,975 --> 00:22:50,764
我不懂你在說什麼
I have no idea what you're talking about.

251
00:22:50,848 --> 00:22:53,559
等等 什麼，你現在可以看到他了？
Wait. What, so you can see him now?

252
00:22:53,642 --> 00:22:55,519
- 什麼？我當然能看到他  - 可我以為…
- What? Of course I can see him. - But I thought...

253
00:22:55,603 --> 00:22:57,271
- 不…  - 你說什麼呢？
- No... - What are you talking about?

254
00:22:57,354 --> 00:22:58,898
我被搞糊塗了
This is so confusing.

255
00:22:59,648 --> 00:23:00,816
這是誰？
Who's this?

256
00:23:01,358 --> 00:23:03,360
我爸爸，我兩歲時他就死了
That's my dad. He died when I was two.

257
00:23:09,950 --> 00:23:11,535
克拉蕾，等等
Clary, a moment.

258
00:23:11,619 --> 00:23:13,778
等等，你媽消失了
So, wait, your mom is gone,

259
00:23:14,376 --> 00:23:18,500
你卻跟這染金髮的追星小伙在一起？
and you're hanging around with some dyed-blond wannabe Goth weirdo?

260
00:23:19,209 --> 00:23:20,794
你在哪兒遇到他的？
Where'd you come across this guy?

261
00:23:20,878 --> 00:23:24,340
- 不，我沒有 是他找我的  - 什麼？他找你
- No, I didn't. He found me. - What? He found you?

262
00:23:24,423 --> 00:23:26,717
- 不，我知道這聽起來…  - 看看這個
- No, I know it sounds... - You should check this.

263
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,969
鄭重聲明，我頭髮金色是天生的
And for the record, my hair is naturally blond.

264
00:23:31,597 --> 00:23:34,850
克拉蕾，克拉蕾，克拉蕾… 西蒙？
Clary, Clary, Clary... Simon?

265
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:36,644
她打過電話？
She called you?

266
00:23:38,145 --> 00:23:39,480
你為什麼不接？
Why didn't you pick up?

267
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:42,191
要是知道這麼嚴重，我早接了
If I'd known it was serious, I would have picked up.

268
00:23:42,274 --> 00:23:44,360
你都沒接怎麼會知道？
Well, how would you know if you didn't pick it up?

269
00:23:47,363 --> 00:23:48,781
那是什麼？
What's that?

270
00:23:51,742 --> 00:23:53,118
沒好事
Nothing good.

271
00:23:53,661 --> 00:23:55,621
你懂她哪兒弄來這個的嗎？
Do you have any idea where she got this?

272
00:23:55,704 --> 00:23:57,498
我得找盧克
I've got to find Luke.

273
00:24:08,717 --> 00:24:10,636
太奇怪了，他車在這兒
It's so weird. His truck's here.

274
00:24:10,928 --> 00:24:12,262
來吧 這邊
Come on. This way.

275
00:24:14,473 --> 00:24:15,816
不，你在這等
No, you wait here.

276
00:24:15,816 --> 00:24:17,351
幹嘛要聽你的？
Who made you the boss?

277
00:24:18,102 --> 00:24:20,896
沒關係，這樣有人來能通知我們
It's okay. Just let us know if anyone comes.

278
00:24:21,730 --> 00:24:23,805
我認識盧克好多年
I've known Luke all these years,

279
00:24:23,805 --> 00:24:25,693
但我都沒下來過
but I've never been down here.

280
00:24:35,327 --> 00:24:36,495
什麼？
What?

281
00:24:37,037 --> 00:24:38,580
快點，夥計！
Come on, mate!

282
00:24:50,342 --> 00:24:52,011
夥計，聽好…
Now, listen...

283
00:24:52,386 --> 00:24:55,347
你要做的就是說真話
All you got to do, mate, is tell me the truth.

284
00:24:55,431 --> 00:24:57,850
我說了，不知道聖盃在哪兒
I'm telling you, I don't know where the Cup is.

285
00:24:57,933 --> 00:25:00,060
我知道你和喬絲關繫好
I know you and Jocie are close.

286
00:25:00,144 --> 00:25:01,937
我可不是傻子？
I'm not stupid, am I?

287
00:25:02,396 --> 00:25:04,064
別這樣回答
Don't answer that.

288
00:25:04,398 --> 00:25:05,641
聽我說，夥計
Listen to me, mate.

289
00:25:05,641 --> 00:25:07,943
只要告訴我聖盃在哪兒
Just tell me where the Mortal Cup is.

290
00:25:08,652 --> 00:25:10,529
喬絲就會沒事
And then Jocie will be fine.

291
00:25:10,612 --> 00:25:13,164
盧克，說啊，告訴我
Lukey, tell me. Tell me the truth.

292
00:25:13,164 --> 00:25:14,199
我不知道
I don't know.

293
00:25:14,283 --> 00:25:16,368
你可別惹我生氣
You don't want to make me angry.

294
00:25:16,452 --> 00:25:18,662
- 我說了…  - 是嗎？
- I'm telling you... - Do you?

295
00:25:19,955 --> 00:25:22,198
