I'm going to ask you again, mate,

296
00:25:22,198 --> 00:25:23,584
聖盃在哪兒？
where's the Cup, huh?

297
00:25:23,667 --> 00:25:25,169
我不知道
I don't know.

298
00:25:25,335 --> 00:25:28,839
我們都需要它，盧克，不是嗎？
We all want the same thing, Lukey boy, don't we?

299
00:25:28,922 --> 00:25:32,509
不同之處，我覺得你知道它在哪兒
Difference is, I think you know where it is.

300
00:25:32,718 --> 00:25:33,886
不是嗎？
Don't you?

301
00:25:33,969 --> 00:25:35,971
快點 快點 說啊！
Come on. Come on. Talk!

302
00:25:36,055 --> 00:25:38,807
- 我們得走了  - 不，求你了，你要幫他
- We need to go. - No, please, you have to help him.

303
00:25:38,891 --> 00:25:40,184
你不懂
You don't understand.

304
00:25:40,976 --> 00:25:42,561
