I don't want her back.

324
00:26:36,073 --> 00:26:37,658
我一點不在乎
I couldn't care less.

325
00:26:37,741 --> 00:26:40,100
我這麼多年
I have spent years

326
00:26:40,100 --> 00:26:43,080
