I don't believe you. Do you believe him?

332
00:27:05,602 --> 00:27:07,146
- 克拉蕾，快跑！  - 克拉蕾，聽我說！
- Clary, run!          - Clary, listen!

333
00:27:18,866 --> 00:27:21,034
