He's been picking me up at school for years.

347
00:28:54,503 --> 00:28:57,172
也許這記憶不真實
Look, maybe those memories aren't real.

348
00:28:57,714 --> 00:28:59,841
你不記得我說的了嗎？
Do you remember what I told you?

349
00:28:59,925 --> 00:29:01,843
誰都不能相信
You can't trust anyone.

350
00:29:03,178 --> 00:29:04,721
不，我要找回媽媽，我要回家
No, I need to find my mom. I have to go home.

351
00:29:04,805 --> 00:29:06,932
- 我肯定漏了什麼！  - 聽我說，好嗎？
- There must be something that I missed! - Listen to me, okay?

352
00:29:07,015 --> 00:29:09,017
我們會弄清的，但不是此時此地
We'll figure this out, but not here and not now.

353
00:29:09,101 --> 00:29:11,728
