and I will protect you with my life.

356
00:29:16,525 --> 00:29:18,819
你們在這兒，我以為你們緊跟著
There you guys are. I thought you were right behind me.

357
00:29:18,902 --> 00:29:20,404
我丟了你們
I thought I'd lost you.

358
00:29:20,487 --> 00:29:22,948
好吧，我跟著你
Okay. I'll follow you.

359
00:29:23,031 --> 00:29:25,242
你確定嗎？他剛殺了兩個警察
Are you sure about that? 'Cause he just killed two cops.

360
00:29:25,325 --> 00:29:26,535
呀，他們不是警察
Yeah, they weren't cops.

361
00:29:27,577 --> 00:29:29,621
我覺得他們就是
