01:00:00,992 --> 01:00:02,536
要救西蒙，而傑斯…
I mean, we had to save Simon, and Jace...

726
01:00:02,619 --> 01:00:04,704
傑斯應該拯救世界
Jace thinks he needs to save the world.

727
01:00:05,330 --> 01:00:08,250
但你沒鼓勵他這麼做
But you don't need to encourage him to do it.

728
01:00:08,333 --> 01:00:09,300
這就是你們要做的
But that's what you guys do.

729
01:00:09,384 --> 01:00:13,171
對，我們　要做的
Yes, us. What we do.

730
01:00:13,588 --> 01:00:15,590
我們是團隊，你是累贅
We're a team, you're deadweight.

731
01:00:16,550 --> 01:00:18,802
- 凡人  - 我不是凡人
- A mundane. - I'm not a mundane.

732
01:00:19,928 --> 01:00:22,035
你要是表現得有半點勇敢
And if you were half as brave as you pretend to be,

733
01:00:22,035 --> 01:00:22,806
就得承認…
you'd admit that...

734
01:00:22,889 --> 01:00:24,224
什麼？
What?

735
01:00:24,683 --> 01:00:26,386
你承認你愛上了傑斯
You'd admit that you're in love with Jace,

736
01:00:26,386 --> 01:00:27,853
這才是千真萬確的
and that's what this is really about.

737
01:00:29,563 --> 01:00:32,566
你敢再這樣說一下…
If you ever say anything like that again...

738
01:00:33,900 --> 01:00:35,527
我定殺死你
I'll kill you.

739
01:01:01,845 --> 01:01:04,306
- 我暈了多久？  - 一整天
- How long was I out? - All day.

740
01:01:04,389 --> 01:01:05,891
你的眼鏡
Found your glasses.

741
01:01:05,974 --> 01:01:07,934
- 有一邊鏡片裂了  - 嗯
- One of the lenses cracked. - Yeah.

742
01:01:16,985 --> 01:01:18,695
好神奇
How weird.

743
01:01:21,531 --> 01:01:23,408
我似乎不需要它了
I don't seem to need them anymore.

744
01:01:26,453 --> 01:01:29,039
那你在畫什麼？
So, what are you drawing?

745
01:01:30,373 --> 01:01:31,708
沒什麼
Nothing.

746
01:01:41,843 --> 01:01:43,887
- 你還好嗎？  - 還好
- You okay?     - Yeah.

747
01:01:43,970 --> 01:01:45,305
這太瘋狂了
It was crazy.

748
01:01:49,309 --> 01:01:51,311
對不起之前我不相信你
I'm sorry I didn't believe you before.

749
01:01:51,394 --> 01:01:52,896
現在我信了
Now I get it.

750
01:01:54,814 --> 01:01:56,149
還有…
And...

751
01:01:57,484 --> 01:01:59,903
當時我昏倒了
And I must have passed out,

752
01:02:00,779 --> 01:02:02,155
接著你就出現
and then you showed up.

753
01:02:03,073 --> 01:02:04,616
聽著
Listen,

754
01:02:04,699 --> 01:02:08,203
我知道我總是那個要被依賴的人
I know I've always been the one who needed you

755
01:02:08,286 --> 01:02:09,621
比起你依賴我來
more than you needed me.

756
01:02:09,704 --> 01:02:11,248
- 不是真的  - 是真的
- That's not true. - Yes, it is,

757
01:02:11,331 --> 01:02:12,832
但我不在乎
but I never cared.

758
01:02:20,048 --> 01:02:23,176
我只有媽媽，盧克和你了
I've only ever had my mom, Luke and you.

759
01:02:23,927 --> 01:02:26,930
別亂想你對我來說不重要
Don't ever imagine that you weren't important to me.

760
01:02:28,014 --> 01:02:29,599
- 好吧  - 好吧
- Okay.   - Okay.

761
01:03:13,101 --> 01:03:15,103
你跟鋼琴有仇嗎？
What did that piano ever do to you?

762
01:03:15,186 --> 01:03:17,564
好像失去唯一真愛一樣
You play it like you've lost your only love.

763
01:03:17,939 --> 01:03:20,317
不幸的是我唯一真愛就是自己
Unfortunately, my one true love remains myself.

764
01:03:20,400 --> 01:03:22,152
至少你不用愁遭拒絕
Well, at least you don't have to worry about rejection.

765
01:03:22,235 --> 01:03:23,091
那也不一定
Not necessarily.

766
01:03:23,091 --> 01:03:26,114
我有時會自我分裂，尋求刺激
I turn myself down occasionally just to keep it interesting.

767
01:03:26,406 --> 01:03:28,158
你彈得很有熱情
You do play that with a lot of passion.

768
01:03:28,241 --> 01:03:29,419
這才有問題
Well, that's the problem.

769
01:03:29,419 --> 01:03:30,869
我不該投入太多感情
I play it with too much emotion.

770
01:03:30,952 --> 01:03:34,196
本應該只是簡單地音符重現
It's supposed to be played with a simple representation of notes,

771
01:03:34,196 --> 01:03:35,081
而不是詮釋
no interpretation.

772
01:03:38,710 --> 01:03:41,254
音樂就該有感情
Music is supposed to have emotion.

773
01:03:43,923 --> 01:03:47,344
邪靈對交錯的音調才有反應
Demons react to certain frequencies when two tones cross.

774
01:03:48,428 --> 01:03:49,637
才能使他們癲狂
Drives them crazy.

775
01:03:52,932 --> 01:03:55,810
看，巴赫發現這點並構建了一個體系
See, Bach discovered this and put it into a system using

776
01:03:55,894 --> 01:03:58,688
用數字序列融合音調
a mathematical progression of tonal combinations

777
01:03:58,772 --> 01:04:00,607
可以顯現邪靈
that allows us to expose demons.

778
01:04:05,362 --> 01:04:07,364
那巴赫也是個暗影獵人咯？
So Bach was a Shadowhunter?

779
01:04:07,447 --> 01:04:09,491
- 是的  - 這麼說…
- Yes.        - So...

780
01:04:10,158 --> 01:04:14,704
巴赫對於邪靈們就像大蒜對於吸血鬼
Bach is to demons what garlic is to vampires.

781
01:04:15,789 --> 01:04:17,123
也對吧
Kind of.

782
01:04:17,207 --> 01:04:19,209
我是說：大蒜會被用盡
I mean, you can run out of garlic.

783
01:04:19,292 --> 01:04:21,127
但音樂卻無止境
You can't really run out of music.

784
01:04:24,798 --> 01:04:27,133
那�放著你的玩意嗎？
Is that where you keep all your toys?

785
01:04:28,968 --> 01:04:30,470
有趣得多
It's way more fun.

786
01:04:30,845 --> 01:04:32,097
來吧
Come on.

787
01:04:32,180 --> 01:04:33,848
這是穿梭門
It's a portal.

788
01:04:33,932 --> 01:04:36,184
像百慕大一樣的自然現象
Like the Bermuda Triangle, it's a natural phenomenon.

789
01:04:36,267 --> 01:04:38,144
神院圍繞它而建
The Institute was built around it.

790
01:04:38,561 --> 01:04:41,815
據說神院是紐約最早的建築
Some say that the Institute was the first building in New York.

791
01:04:43,233 --> 01:04:44,275
所以它…
So it's...

792
01:04:44,359 --> 01:04:46,694
空間不都只是直線型的
Dimensions aren't all just straight lines.

793
01:04:46,778 --> 01:04:48,405
也會有彎曲
There's bends,

794
01:04:48,488 --> 01:04:50,073
折疊，凹角
folds and nooks.

795
01:04:50,657 --> 01:04:53,368
有點難以解釋，不過
It's a little bit difficult to explain, but

796
01:04:53,618 --> 01:04:57,163
穿梭門能帶你到任何你想去的地方
the Portal can take you wherever you want to go in this dimension.

797
01:04:59,499 --> 01:05:01,501
一旦穿過表面
So, as soon as you break that surface,

798
01:05:01,584 --> 01:05:04,003
你就會被送到你心底最深處
you're transported to wherever your deepest thoughts lie.

799
01:05:04,087 --> 01:05:05,130
那意味著…
So that means...

800
01:05:05,213 --> 01:05:06,923
- 我媽媽…  - 等下
- My mom... - Wait.

801
01:05:07,674 --> 01:05:10,427
我們訓練一生才懂得使用它
We spend our entire lives training how to use it,

802
01:05:10,510 --> 01:05:13,012
進入前要先想像一下所去之處
visualizing where it will take us before we step into it,

803
01:05:13,096 --> 01:05:15,432
那必須要非常集中精力
and that takes incredible focus.

804
01:05:18,852 --> 01:05:21,604
如果沒有經過正確訓練而進入的話
If you were to step into it without the proper training,

805
01:05:21,688 --> 01:05:23,466
你將永無安定
you could end up in limbo,

806
01:05:23,466 --> 01:05:25,442
永生困在記憶之中
lost in your own mind forever.

807
01:05:28,570 --> 01:05:29,737
這兒
Here.

808
01:05:29,821 --> 01:05:31,614
我做給你看
Let me show you.

809
01:05:31,698 --> 01:05:32,991
快點
Come on.

810
01:05:35,869 --> 01:05:37,036
別偷看
No peeking.

811
01:06:14,199 --> 01:06:15,575
很酷吧，對吧？
Pretty cool, isn't it?

812
01:06:16,618 --> 01:06:18,077
現在…
Now...

813
01:06:18,912 --> 01:06:21,289
你和我…
You and I...

814
01:06:21,831 --> 01:06:23,458
要慶祝你的生日
Have a birthday to celebrate.

815
01:06:23,541 --> 01:06:24,876
你怎麼知道？
How did you know?

816
01:06:24,959 --> 01:06:27,670
我之前找你，就查到過
Research. When I was trying to find you.

817
01:06:32,217 --> 01:06:34,135
不會有人來這兒
No one comes up here anymore.

818
01:06:34,219 --> 01:06:35,929
這�屬於我們
We have the place to ourselves.

819
01:06:36,679 --> 01:06:38,890
美得窒息了
This is breathtaking.

820
01:07:00,954 --> 01:07:02,330
抱歉，沒有蛋糕
Sorry there's no cake.

821
01:07:02,413 --> 01:07:04,666
我原本就沒期望
Well, I was expecting nothing,

822
01:07:04,749 --> 01:07:06,417
這已很棒了
so this is great.

823
01:07:07,210 --> 01:07:10,004
不過，每個人都該在生日那天得到些什麼
Well, everyone should get something for their birthday.

824
01:07:14,467 --> 01:07:16,177
你生日得到什麼？
What did you get?

825
01:07:16,261 --> 01:07:18,263
大多數是武器
Weapons mostly.

826
01:07:19,806 --> 01:07:21,391
希望沒讓你吃驚
I'm sure that doesn't surprise you.

827
01:07:21,474 --> 01:07:23,309
現在沒有什麼會讓我吃驚
At this point, nothing really does.

828
01:07:26,229 --> 01:07:28,731
當我九歲時…
When I was nine...

829
01:07:30,066 --> 01:07:31,818
我父親送了我一隻隼
My father gave me a falcon.

830
01:07:32,110 --> 01:07:33,778
他要我讓它聽話
He told me to make it obedient.

831
01:07:33,861 --> 01:07:35,989
我本該弄瞎那隻鳥
I was supposed to keep the bird blind,

832
01:07:36,072 --> 01:07:38,157
但我做不到
but I couldn't bring myself to do it.

833
01:07:39,033 --> 01:07:41,247
相反的是，我撫摸它的翅膀
Instead, I touched and stroked its wings

834
01:07:41,247 --> 01:07:42,328
直到它信任我
until it trusted me.

835
01:07:42,620 --> 01:07:44,581
我以為完美地馴服了它
I tamed it to perfection.

836
01:07:45,665 --> 01:07:47,263
我把它帶給父親
I took it to my father,

837
01:07:47,263 --> 01:07:50,128
希望父親為我所做的感到驕傲
expecting him to be proud of what I'd done.

838
01:07:50,503 --> 01:07:52,255
他說：
He said,

839
01:07:52,505 --> 01:07:54,591
「我是要你讓他聽話」
"I told you to make it obedient.

840
01:07:55,675 --> 01:07:57,552
「不是要你教它愛你」
"Instead, you taught it to love you.

841
01:07:57,927 --> 01:07:59,804
「你沒有馴服它，你毀了它」
"You didn't tame it, you broke it."

842
01:08:00,930 --> 01:08:03,474
他帶走鳥，並割了它的脖子
Then he took the bird and he broke its neck.

843
01:08:05,184 --> 01:08:07,437
我當時哭了整整一夜，此後再沒哭過
I cried all night and I never cried again.

844
01:08:07,937 --> 01:08:09,772
你原諒他嗎？
Did you ever forgive him?

845
01:08:11,316 --> 01:08:13,192
他這麼做是要我強大
He did it to make me stronger.

846
01:08:18,740 --> 01:08:20,241
那是你名字維蘭德的意義嗎？
Does that stand for Wayland?

847
01:08:26,956 --> 01:08:28,333
午夜
Midnight.

848
01:08:28,875 --> 01:08:30,293
瞧瞧這些
Watch this.

849
01:08:48,895 --> 01:08:50,938
一個女孩說要一顆大寶石
When a girl says she wants a big rock,

850
01:08:51,022 --> 01:08:53,274
但她並非就是這個意思
she doesn't literally mean a big rock.

851
01:08:53,358 --> 01:08:56,110
每個暗影獵人都有屬於自己的魔石
Every Shadowhunter should have their own witchlight.

852
01:09:05,161 --> 01:09:06,663
有人在
We have company.

853
01:09:07,914 --> 01:09:09,415
那只是霍奇的鳥
That's Hodge's bird.

854
01:09:12,251 --> 01:09:13,544
我們得走了
We should probably go.

855
01:09:55,795 --> 01:09:57,004
是啊
Yeah.

856
01:09:57,797 --> 01:09:59,298
我們真得走了
We should definitely go.

857
01:10:18,151 --> 01:10:20,445
抱歉忘記告訴你會定時噴水
Sorry about the sprinkler system.

858
01:10:20,862 --> 01:10:22,155
別提它了
I forgot about that.

859
01:10:25,575 --> 01:10:26,784
要去睡了嗎？
You going to sleep?

860
01:10:26,868 --> 01:10:28,327
累了嗎？
Well, aren't you tired?

861
01:10:28,786 --> 01:10:30,496
我從沒這樣清醒
I've never been more awake.

862
01:10:36,627 --> 01:10:38,671
- 西蒙，我以為你…  - 睡了？
- Simon, I thought you were... - Asleep?

863
01:10:38,838 --> 01:10:40,006
之前是的
Yeah, I was.

864
01:10:40,423 --> 01:10:41,632
我們只不過…
We were just...

865
01:10:41,716 --> 01:10:43,158
下次，最好是
Next time, it might be a nice idea

866
01:10:43,158 --> 01:10:45,261
你得說你已經有個男人在床上
to mention that you already have a man in your bed,

867
01:10:45,344 --> 01:10:47,013
我們才不會這麼尷尬了
so we can avoid such uncomfortable situations.

868
01:10:47,096 --> 01:10:48,058
你讓他到你床上？
You invited him to bed?

869
01:10:48,058 --> 01:10:49,390
我知道這挺荒唐的，是不是？
I know, it's ridiculous, isn't it?

870
01:10:49,474 --> 01:10:50,683
不可能一切合心意
We would never have all fit.

871
01:10:50,767 --> 01:10:52,643
我沒有讓他到我床上
I didn't invite him into bed.

872
01:10:52,727 --> 01:10:54,520
只是接吻而已
We were just kissing.

873
01:10:55,980 --> 01:10:57,774
你太快丟掉我倆的愛了
How swiftly you dismiss our love.

874
01:10:58,191 --> 01:10:59,358
傑斯…
Jace...

875
01:10:59,525 --> 01:11:01,152
西蒙，很晚了，對不起吵醒你
Simon, it's late, and I'm sorry we woke you.

876
01:11:01,235 --> 01:11:02,528
我也是
So am I.

877
01:11:04,530 --> 01:11:07,011
去吧，去找他，去向他道歉
Go ahead. Go after him, go apologize to him,

878
01:11:07,011 --> 01:11:09,327
去跟他說他才是特別的
go tell him just how special he really is.

879
01:11:09,410 --> 01:11:11,245
- 別這樣！  - 哪樣了？
- Stop acting like that! - Like what?

880
01:11:11,329 --> 01:11:12,651
好像你沒受傷一樣
Like nothing ever hurts you.

881
01:11:12,651 --> 01:11:14,994
嗯，也許你應該想清楚的
Well, maybe you should have thought about that

882
01:11:14,994 --> 01:11:16,042
在你親我之前
before you kissed me.

883
01:11:16,125 --> 01:11:17,460
是我親你？
I kissed you?

884
01:11:18,211 --> 01:11:20,880
別擔心，這對我也沒什麼了不起
Don't worry, it wasn't that special for me either.

885
01:11:26,219 --> 01:11:28,638
西蒙，真的很抱歉，我還以為你在…
I'm really sorry, Simon, but weren't you just in the...

886
01:11:28,721 --> 01:11:30,389
我只是在找你
I was just looking for you.

887
01:11:30,973 --> 01:11:32,809
- 你要去哪兒？  - 回家
- Where are you going? - Home.

888
01:11:32,892 --> 01:11:34,727
顯然我在這太久，不受歡迎了
It's clear I overstayed my welcome.

889
01:11:34,811 --> 01:11:37,104
對不起，這對我也太突然了
Look, I'm sorry, okay? It wasn't like it was planned.

890
01:11:37,188 --> 01:11:39,732
但就是發生了，拜託
Let me guess, it just happened. Please.

891
01:11:39,816 --> 01:11:41,484
聽著，我知道你不喜歡他，但是…
Look, I know you don't like him, but...

892
01:11:41,567 --> 01:11:43,736
其實我恨他
Actually, I hate the guy.

893
01:11:44,070 --> 01:11:45,238
為什麼？
Why?

894
01:11:45,321 --> 01:11:46,614
我以為你不至於愛上他
I thought you were better than that.

895
01:11:46,697 --> 01:11:48,449
那這又說明什麼？
What's that supposed to mean?

896
01:11:48,574 --> 01:11:51,869
我才是一直等你的人，不是他
I'm the one who's always been there for you, not him.

897
01:12:01,254 --> 01:12:03,047
我早愛上你了
I'm in love with you.

898
01:12:13,474 --> 01:12:16,477
不過顯然你沒有同感
And it's clear that you don't feel the same way.

899
01:12:18,437 --> 01:12:19,772
- 這…  - 不
- It's... - Don't.

900
01:12:20,147 --> 01:12:21,983
沒什麼好說了
There's nothing to say.

901
01:12:25,486 --> 01:12:26,988
還有，克拉蕾
And, Clary,

902
01:12:27,071 --> 01:12:29,240
他只是利用你獲得聖盃
he's just using you to get the Cup.

903
01:12:35,121 --> 01:12:36,497
西蒙…
Simon...

904
01:14:30,903 --> 01:14:33,990
你母親也能這麼做
Your mother was the only other person who could do that.

905
01:14:34,615 --> 01:14:36,909
但我之前從沒這麼做過
But I've never been able to do this before.

906
01:14:37,702 --> 01:14:41,163
說明封印住的不僅是你的回憶
Apparently the block wasn't just repressing your memories,

907
01:14:41,247 --> 01:14:43,124
還有你的能力
but your abilities as well.

908
01:15:03,602 --> 01:15:05,563
- 傑斯，我…  - 別跟我說
- Jace, I... - Don't tell me.

909
01:15:05,646 --> 01:15:08,315
你急需一個裸模來畫畫
You have a drawing emergency and you need a nude model.

910
01:15:08,399 --> 01:15:10,651
- 沒那個心情  - 聽著！
- I'm not in the mood. - Listen!

911
01:15:11,277 --> 01:15:13,612
我知道我媽媽將聖盃藏哪兒了
I know where my mom hid the Cup.

912
01:15:26,792 --> 01:15:27,877
克拉蕾…
Clary...

913
01:15:27,960 --> 01:15:29,920
你看上去很不同
Wow, you look different.

914
01:15:30,004 --> 01:15:32,173
嗯，這只是我借來的
Yeah, it's just something I borrowed.

915
01:15:33,090 --> 01:15:36,385
我是說，你穿得很漂亮
I mean, nice outfit. It's good.

916
01:15:36,469 --> 01:15:38,304
好吧，現在我沒空聊 抱歉
Yeah, I can't talk now. Sorry.

917
01:15:47,860 --> 01:15:50,370
（西蒙，克拉蕾剛進她家）

918
01:16:10,836 --> 01:16:13,255
- 克拉蕾  - 我來拿塔羅牌
- Clary. - I came for the tarot cards.

919
01:16:13,672 --> 01:16:14,882
- 為什麼？  - 我需要他們
- Why?          - I need them.

920
01:16:14,965 --> 01:16:16,926
你懂的，就是我媽媽畫的那些？
You know, the ones that Mom painted?

921
01:16:17,009 --> 01:16:19,146
我就想快點看看
I just need to look at them really quickly,

922
01:16:19,146 --> 01:16:20,846
然後就還你，我發誓
and I'll give them back, I promise.

923
01:16:21,388 --> 01:16:22,848
武器別帶進來
Those can't come in here.

924
01:16:23,349 --> 01:16:25,017
這是和平之地
This is a peaceful house.

925
01:16:25,810 --> 01:16:27,186
放那兒
Put them in there.

926
01:17:14,900 --> 01:17:16,026
今天感覺怎麼樣？
How are you feeling today?

927
01:17:19,405 --> 01:17:21,699
很好，很好
Fine. Just fine.

928
01:17:47,892 --> 01:17:50,519
小伙子，走調了
Young man, that piano is out of tune.

929
01:17:52,104 --> 01:17:53,564
拜託別彈了
Please don't.

930
01:18:05,784 --> 01:18:07,244
小伙子
Young man.

931
01:18:10,789 --> 01:18:12,124
別彈！
Stop!

932
01:18:24,136 --> 01:18:25,471
那首曲
That song.

933
01:18:27,139 --> 01:18:28,891
不是我的最愛
Not one of my favorites.

934
01:18:50,829 --> 01:18:52,289
停下來！
Stop!

935
01:18:52,957 --> 01:18:54,250
拿來看看
Let's have a look.

936
01:19:44,049 --> 01:19:45,050
快跑！
Get out!

937
01:20:17,249 --> 01:20:18,822
你好，多蘿西夫人
Hey, Madame Dorothea.

938
01:20:18,822 --> 01:20:20,252
有看見克拉蕾嗎？
Have you seen Clary?

939
01:20:20,336 --> 01:20:22,171
我剛收到短信說她在這兒
I just got a text that said she was here.

940
01:20:22,254 --> 01:20:23,505
沒有
No.

941
01:20:23,589 --> 01:20:25,424
好吧，我只是…
Okay. Well, I'll just...

942
01:20:25,591 --> 01:20:27,009
西蒙！
Simon!

943
01:20:27,926 --> 01:20:29,428
西蒙！
Simon!

944
01:20:30,220 --> 01:20:31,513
西蒙！
Simon!

945
01:20:31,597 --> 01:20:33,599
西蒙，這不是真的她！
Simon, it's not really her!

946
01:20:35,184 --> 01:20:36,185
西蒙！
Simon!

947
01:20:37,227 --> 01:20:38,604
西蒙！
Simon!

948
01:20:43,859 --> 01:20:45,277
我來照顧他
I'll take care of him.

949
01:20:46,403 --> 01:20:47,446
西蒙！
Simon!

950
01:20:47,529 --> 01:20:49,406
她拿走了聖盃！
She's got the Cup!

951
01:21:03,253 --> 01:21:04,421
西蒙！
Simon!

952
01:21:50,968 --> 01:21:52,136
對不起
I'm sorry.

953
01:21:52,219 --> 01:21:53,929
對不起
I'm sorry.

954
01:22:06,024 --> 01:22:07,526
傑斯！
Jace!

955
01:22:11,697 --> 01:22:13,699
圖符不起作用
The runes aren't working.

956
01:22:19,538 --> 01:22:21,331
西蒙，跟著我
Simon, you follow me.

957
01:22:29,715 --> 01:22:31,049
把他們切碎
You cut these up.

958
01:22:33,760 --> 01:22:34,909
不要 夠了
Don't. You've done enough.

959
01:22:34,909 --> 01:22:36,972
別這樣對她 這不是她的錯
Don't talk to her like that. This isn't her fault.

960
01:22:37,055 --> 01:22:38,932
- 不，你說的對，是你的錯  - 伊莎貝爾！
- No, you're right. This is your fault. - Isabelle!

961
01:22:39,016 --> 01:22:40,893
亞力克一直都告誡你你會受傷
Alec kept telling you that you were going to get hurt.

962
01:22:40,976 --> 01:22:42,788
你會讓我們都受傷
You were going to get us all hurt.

963
01:22:42,788 --> 01:22:43,979
現在他卻快死了
Now he's the one dying.

964
01:22:44,062 --> 01:22:45,439
我們需要找到聖盃
Well, we needed to get the Mortal Cup.

965
01:22:45,522 --> 01:22:46,961
但還有別的辦法
But there were other ways to do it

966
01:22:46,961 --> 01:22:48,484
沒必要為此傷害你的摯友
than getting your best friend killed.

967
01:22:50,861 --> 01:22:52,404
去找霍奇
Why don't you go get Hodge.

968
01:22:53,864 --> 01:22:55,741
我從沒想讓亞力克這樣
I never wanted anything to happen to Alec.

969
01:22:55,824 --> 01:22:57,242
對不起
I'm sorry.

970
01:23:01,914 --> 01:23:04,708
我們同意一起做的，我們一個團隊
We agreed to do this together. We're a team.

971
01:23:04,791 --> 01:23:07,211
有了克拉蕾，我們就不是一個團隊了
Since Clary got here, we haven't been a team.

972
01:23:11,924 --> 01:23:13,217
霍奇
Hodge!

973
01:23:13,759 --> 01:23:15,177
霍奇
Hodge!

974
01:23:16,053 --> 01:23:17,513
亞力克受傷了
Alec's getting worse.

975
01:23:17,596 --> 01:23:18,764
我知道
I know.

976
01:23:19,848 --> 01:23:21,808
我已經叫人來了
I've already sent for someone.

977
01:23:23,435 --> 01:23:25,229
你得到聖盃了嗎？
Did you get the Cup?

978
01:23:48,794 --> 01:23:50,295
然後呢？
What now?

979
01:23:55,300 --> 01:23:56,593
霍奇？
Hodge?

980
01:24:03,016 --> 01:24:05,561
你根本不知道
You have no idea what it's like

981
01:24:05,644 --> 01:24:08,146
克拉夫的詛咒是什麼滋味
living with the Clave's curse,

982
01:24:08,230 --> 01:24:10,983
不能從這兒踏出一步
unable to set so much as a foot outside,

983
01:24:11,858 --> 01:24:14,319
連開窗戶都害怕
afraid to even open a window.

984
01:24:17,155 --> 01:24:19,241
克拉蕾，別太怪我
Try not to judge me too harshly, Clary.

985
01:24:29,209 --> 01:24:30,669
霍奇，你要做什麼？
Hodge, what have you done?

986
01:24:54,484 --> 01:24:56,778
我知道你終將把聖盃給我
I always knew you would bring me the Cup.

987
01:24:56,862 --> 01:24:58,614
只是時間問題而已
It was only a matter of time.

988
01:25:01,867 --> 01:25:03,493
我媽媽在哪兒？
Where is she?

989
01:25:05,203 --> 01:25:06,455
她很好
She's fine.

990
01:25:10,667 --> 01:25:12,669
你得到了想要的，現在放她走
You got what you want. Now let her go.

991
01:25:12,753 --> 01:25:15,339
我得看看這是不是真的
I have to make sure you gave me the real one.

992
01:25:17,883 --> 01:25:20,385
每個人為了聖盃都會不擇手段
Everybody wants the Cup for the wrong reason.

993
01:25:23,138 --> 01:25:24,473
那你沒有嗎？
And you don't?

994
01:25:24,556 --> 01:25:25,932
擁有它
With this Cup,

995
01:25:26,016 --> 01:25:28,644
我才能淨化我的血統
I can cleanse our bloodlines,

996
01:25:28,727 --> 01:25:30,812
拯救我們的種族
Save our race.

997
01:25:30,896 --> 01:25:34,483
你也許不太瞭解人類歷史
You might not know much about mundane history,

998
01:25:34,566 --> 01:25:38,502
聽著，當人們談論保護種族時
but I can tell you when people start talking about preserving a race,

999
01:25:38,502 --> 01:25:39,571
從沒好事發生
it never goes well.

1000
01:25:41,239 --> 01:25:44,409
這就是為何我媽媽要用一生時間隱瞞你
That's why my mom spent her whole life hiding it from you.

1001
01:25:44,493 --> 01:25:45,744
不
No.

1002
01:25:47,079 --> 01:25:49,081
她不是要藏聖盃
She wasn't hiding the Cup.

1003
01:25:49,581 --> 01:25:51,333
她是要藏著你
She was hiding you.

1004
01:25:53,418 --> 01:25:54,461
喝下去
Drink.

1005
01:25:54,544 --> 01:25:56,421
我不會喝的
I'm not gonna drink that.

1006
01:25:56,505 --> 01:25:57,923
你為什麼這麼害怕？
Why are you so afraid?

1007
01:25:58,048 --> 01:26:00,676
你還沒出生就已經喝過它了
You've been drinking this since before you were born.

1008
01:26:00,759 --> 01:26:03,845
我在你媽媽懷孕時就給她喝過
I fed it to your mother while you were in her womb.

1009
01:26:06,515 --> 01:26:08,016
快點，克拉蕾
Come on, Clary.

1010
01:26:08,100 --> 01:26:09,851
你現在應該猜到
You must have guessed by now.

1011
01:26:09,935 --> 01:26:11,520
你所有神奇的天賦
All these amazing talents

1012
01:26:11,603 --> 01:26:14,189
都是你母親一直想要壓制的
that your mother so desperately tried to suppress,

1013
01:26:14,272 --> 01:26:16,274
你覺得它從何而來？
where do you think they came from?

1014
01:26:18,360 --> 01:26:20,112
你是我女兒
You're my daughter.

1015
01:26:20,987 --> 01:26:23,824
我的血液流淌在你的身上
My blood runs in your veins.

1016
01:26:24,408 --> 01:26:25,784
現在…
Now...

1017
01:26:26,827 --> 01:26:28,036
喝
Drink.

1018
01:26:31,164 --> 01:26:32,541
快喝！
Drink!

1019
01:26:43,635 --> 01:26:45,303
把它拿出來！
Take that out!

1020
01:26:52,018 --> 01:26:53,520
不！
No!

1021
01:27:05,490 --> 01:27:07,409
有人進入穿梭門了
Someone just went through the Portal.

1022
01:27:07,492 --> 01:27:09,161
我去看看
I'll go check.

1023
01:28:44,464 --> 01:28:45,465
抱歉
Sorry.

1024
01:28:45,549 --> 01:28:46,842
我有點太激動了
I got a bit carried away.

1025
01:28:46,925 --> 01:28:48,134
盧克，你是…
Luke, you're a...

1026
01:28:48,218 --> 01:28:50,804
克拉蕾，聽我說，聽著 別害怕
Clary, listen to me, listen. Don't be afraid.

1027
01:28:50,887 --> 01:28:52,222
- 聽著，好嗎？  - 別碰我！
- Listen, right? - Don't touch me!

1028
01:28:52,305 --> 01:28:54,808
嘿，別這樣
Hey, there's no need for that.

1029
01:28:55,016 --> 01:28:56,768
那東西還會回來
That thing will be back.

1030
01:28:57,727 --> 01:28:59,729
這兒不安全
We are not safe out here.

1031
01:29:02,524 --> 01:29:05,193
我跳進穿梭門，為了躲瓦倫丁
I jumped through the Portal to get away from Valentine.

1032
01:29:05,527 --> 01:29:07,529
我以為會到我媽媽那兒
I thought I'd end up with my mom.

1033
01:29:11,366 --> 01:29:14,703
但是我卻到了最不想來的地方
Instead, I ended up in the last place I wanted to be.

1034
01:29:15,120 --> 01:29:17,622
聽著，穿梭門帶你來
Listen, the Portal brought you here

1035
01:29:17,706 --> 01:29:19,875
說明你一定想到我了
because you must have been thinking of me.

1036
01:29:19,958 --> 01:29:21,877
你內心深處仍信任我
Deep inside, you know you can trust me.

1037
01:29:21,960 --> 01:29:23,231
你說過一點都不在乎
You said you couldn't care

1038
01:29:23,231 --> 01:29:24,880
我們發生什麼事情
less what happened to either of us.

1039
01:29:24,963 --> 01:29:26,590
你跟別人一樣，只是想要聖盃
You just want the Cup, like everyone else.

1040
01:29:26,673 --> 01:29:28,633
我說過要保護你，我還能怎麼做？
I said that to protect you. What else could I do?

1041
01:29:28,717 --> 01:29:31,011
這次我得一直照看你
Been keeping an eye on you this whole time.

1042
01:29:39,019 --> 01:29:40,729
在旅店那兒的是你
That was you at the hotel.

1043
01:29:42,647 --> 01:29:44,566
話說投的好啊
Good throw, by the way.

1044
01:29:49,362 --> 01:29:50,530
我怎麼辦？
What about me?

1045
01:29:50,739 --> 01:29:51,990
你怎麼辦？
What about you?

1046
01:29:52,198 --> 01:29:53,366
我們說好的
We had a deal.

1047
01:29:53,450 --> 01:29:55,827
我仍然沒得到聖盃，不是嗎？
Well, I still don't have my Cup, do I?

1048
01:30:01,541 --> 01:30:03,752
我一直信守諾言
I held up my end of the bargain.

1049
01:30:05,503 --> 01:30:07,088
不，你沒有
No, you didn't.

1050
01:30:07,172 --> 01:30:09,257
我把聖盃給你了
I gave you the Cup.

1051
01:30:09,341 --> 01:30:11,843
是你給克拉蕾的 不是我的錯
You handed it to Clary. That's not my fault.

1052
01:30:11,927 --> 01:30:13,053
幫我解咒
Now lift it.

1053
01:30:15,263 --> 01:30:18,016
聽著，這都是你腦子想的
Listen, it's all in your head.

1054
01:30:18,099 --> 01:30:19,851
不，不！
No. No!

1055
01:30:22,687 --> 01:30:24,397
有詛咒
There's a spell.

1056
01:30:24,481 --> 01:30:26,524
真的？詛咒？
Really? A spell?

1057
01:30:27,025 --> 01:30:29,527
這只是問題的借口
That's just an excuse for a real problem

1058
01:30:29,945 --> 01:30:31,196
在這兒
in there.

1059
01:30:32,656 --> 01:30:34,824
你以為我真的可以解決嗎？
Do you really think I can fix that?

1060
01:30:34,908 --> 01:30:37,452
我給你聖盃了，你幫我帶走恐懼
I give you the Cup, you take away the fear.

1061
01:30:42,207 --> 01:30:44,250
沒有聖盃我也一樣寸步難行
Without the Cup, I'm as stuck as you are.

1062
01:30:45,335 --> 01:30:47,212
我的恐懼才是真的
Except my fear is real.

1063
01:30:47,295 --> 01:30:49,172
每個地下生物
Every Downworlder,

1064
01:30:49,255 --> 01:30:51,007
每個守護者
every member of the Clave,

1065
01:30:51,091 --> 01:30:53,802
每個暗影獵人都在穿梭門另一側
every Shadowhunter on both sides of the Portal

1066
01:30:53,885 --> 01:30:55,637
找我
is looking for me right now.

1067
01:30:55,720 --> 01:30:58,014
我才需要一切幫助
I'm going to need all the help I can get.

1068
01:30:58,390 --> 01:31:01,601
瓦倫丁，你不必這樣的
You don't have to go through with this, Valentine.

1069
01:31:02,185 --> 01:31:04,688
邪靈從來沒到過神院
A demon has never set foot in the Institute.

1070
01:31:06,398 --> 01:31:07,774
現在是時候讓他們來了
Well, maybe it's time they did.

1071
01:31:11,277 --> 01:31:14,823
我等這等好多年了
I've been waiting all these years to do this.

1072
01:31:17,033 --> 01:31:18,827
我別無選擇
Clary's given me no choice.

1073
01:31:22,122 --> 01:31:23,623
她會回來的
She'll come back.

1074
01:31:25,333 --> 01:31:26,543
真的嗎？
Really?

1075
01:31:27,419 --> 01:31:28,920
你敢確定？
And what makes you so sure?

1076
01:31:29,004 --> 01:31:31,923
這兒有她需要的人，像她需要她媽媽一樣
There's someone here she wants as much as her mother.

1077
01:31:32,424 --> 01:31:34,569
你可以騙他們
If you lie and tell them

1078
01:31:34,569 --> 01:31:36,886
說他們都是你的孩子
they're both your children,

1079
01:31:36,970 --> 01:31:39,097
你這樣就能讓他們心碎
you'll break their hearts.

1080
01:31:39,222 --> 01:31:40,765
那又怎麼樣？
What can I say?

1081
01:31:41,057 --> 01:31:43,143
心碎的人最聽話
The broken make the best followers.

1082
01:31:43,810 --> 01:31:45,228
看看你
Look at you.

1083
01:31:45,937 --> 01:31:48,606
愛就是滅亡
To love is to destroy.

1084
01:32:44,746 --> 01:32:46,247
霍奇到底在哪�？
Where the hell is Hodge?

1085
01:32:46,331 --> 01:32:48,041
我們沒多少時間了
We don't have much time.

1086
01:32:50,085 --> 01:32:52,295
- 這弄對了嗎？  - 不
- Does this look right to you? - No.

1087
01:32:55,173 --> 01:32:56,174
快看
Hey, look.

1088
01:32:59,094 --> 01:33:00,512
馬格努斯？
Magnus?

1089
01:33:03,014 --> 01:33:05,850
我需要這些，要很多
I'm going to need all of this. Lots of it.

1090
01:33:08,019 --> 01:33:09,354
拿著
Take this.

1091
01:33:42,887 --> 01:33:44,722
封鎖此地
Lock this place down.

1092
01:33:45,140 --> 01:33:48,476
殺死一切異族
Those who are not allies must be killed.

1093
01:34:03,616 --> 01:34:05,493
別動 它們
Don't do that!

1094
01:34:07,162 --> 01:34:08,496
瓦倫丁
Valentine.

1095
01:34:09,247 --> 01:34:10,498
喬納森
Jonathan.

