我是你爸爸
As your father,

1292
01:54:36,223 --> 01:54:37,849
我求你了
I'm begging you.

1293
01:54:43,772 --> 01:54:45,607
要是我爸爸就一定懂我
If you'd been a real dad,

1294
01:54:45,690 --> 01:54:48,318
懂得聖盃在哪�
you'd know me well enough to imagine where the Cup is,

1295
01:54:48,402 --> 01:54:51,029
知道我心底想的地方
where my deepest thoughts are taking it.

1296
01:54:52,322 --> 01:54:55,117
你一點都不懂我
You don't know the first thing about me.

1297
01:54:56,034 --> 01:54:57,828
你不是我爸…
You're not my dad...

1298
01:54:59,204 --> 01:55:01,039
永遠不是
And you never will be.

1299
01:55:01,123 --> 01:55:03,375
我保證你不會再見到我
I promise, you'll never have to see me again.

1300
01:55:09,923 --> 01:55:11,133
克拉蕾，謝謝
Thank you, Clary.

1301
01:55:15,762 --> 01:55:18,807
沒有聖盃，我們會輸的
Without this Cup, we are lost.

1302
01:55:19,766 --> 01:55:21,017
不是「我們」
Not "we."

1303
01:55:23,311 --> 01:55:24,354
是你
You.

1304
01:55:49,296 --> 01:55:50,464
克拉蕾！
Clary!

1305
01:55:53,550 --> 01:55:55,677
- 不！抓住我！  - 決不！
- No! Don't let go! - Never!

1306
01:55:58,805 --> 01:55:59,890
這兒！
Here!

1307
01:56:58,823 --> 01:57:00,283
你還好嗎？
Are you okay?

1308
01:57:01,117 --> 01:57:02,619
我不知道
I don't know.

1309
01:57:42,284 --> 01:57:44,911
我知道你之前為什麼那樣做了
I understand why you did what you did.

1310
01:57:47,163 --> 01:57:48,832
我原諒你
And I forgive you.

1311
01:57:50,208 --> 01:57:52,168
我要你知道
I want you to know,

1312
01:57:54,254 --> 01:57:56,381
我會為你保密
your secret's safe with me.

1313
01:58:50,143 --> 01:58:52,687
她怎麼樣了？
So, how's she doing?

1314
01:58:53,396 --> 01:58:54,564
情況穩定了
Stable.

1315
01:58:55,231 --> 01:58:57,275
醫生不知道她喝過什麼
The doctors don't know what she took,

1316
01:58:57,359 --> 01:58:59,569
只能等
so we just have to wait.

1317
01:59:03,239 --> 01:59:04,991
對不起
I'm sorry.

1318
01:59:05,075 --> 01:59:07,035
我覺得我只是一個老古董
I guess I'm an old romantic.

1319
01:59:07,118 --> 01:59:09,329
我總希望當我向某人說
I always hoped that when I finally said

1320
01:59:09,412 --> 01:59:12,582
「我愛你」時，她會說同樣的話
"I love you" to someone, she'd say the same thing back.

1321
01:59:13,041 --> 01:59:14,834
那個人會的
And that someone will.

1322
01:59:14,918 --> 01:59:16,252
但願吧
Yeah, I know.

1323
01:59:25,428 --> 01:59:27,097
你很累了
Hey, you're tired.

1324
01:59:27,180 --> 01:59:29,599
去休息吧，我們會照看好她
Go sleep, we'll take care of her.

1325
01:59:30,767 --> 01:59:32,268
好，抱一個
Yeah, come on.

1326
02:00:23,737 --> 02:00:25,780
我喜歡你收拾這�
I like what you've done with the place.

1327
02:00:25,864 --> 02:00:28,324
我只是耍了些把戲
I've got a few tricks up my sleeve.

1328
02:00:30,118 --> 02:00:32,287
克拉蕾，我們真怕你不會回來了
Clary, we're afraid you're not coming back.

1329
02:00:33,830 --> 02:00:35,415
只是現在跟你作伴真的很難
It's just really hard to be around you right now.

1330
02:00:35,498 --> 02:00:37,500
對我來說也一樣
It's hard for me as well.

1331
02:00:38,835 --> 02:00:41,171
但是這不僅僅是我們
But this is about more than us.

1332
02:00:42,464 --> 02:00:45,383
你有不可思議的天賦，我們需要你
You have an incredible gift, and we need you.

1333
02:00:48,470 --> 02:00:49,846
我需要你
I need you.

1334
02:00:51,014 --> 02:00:52,682
我不知道
I just don't know.

1335
02:00:53,349 --> 02:00:55,518
還記得我說過從沒見過天使？
Remember when I said I'd never seen an angel?

1336
02:00:59,731 --> 02:01:01,191
我撒謊了
Well, I lied.

1337
02:01:10,742 --> 02:01:12,744
你是我見過最勇敢的凡人
You're still the bravest mundane I've ever met.

1338
02:01:17,207 --> 02:01:18,875
我可不是凡人
I'm not a mundane.

1339
02:01:21,503 --> 02:01:22,670
等等，傑斯！
Wait, Jace!

1340
02:01:27,008 --> 02:01:28,259
慢慢來啊
You took your time.

1341
02:01:35,225 --> 02:01:37,143
你說過你需要我
You said you needed me.

1342
02:01:42,106 --> 02:01:43,566
你該好好保存它
You should keep that safe.

1343
02:01:43,650 --> 02:01:44,776
我會的
Yeah.

1344
02:01:46,402 --> 02:01:48,112
我可以抱著你嗎…
Is it okay if I...

1345
02:01:49,072 --> 02:01:50,490
我能…
Do I...

1346
02:01:50,573 --> 02:01:52,742
- 這樣可以嗎…  - 沒關係
- Is it okay if I... - Yeah.

1347
02:01:55,995 --> 02:01:58,248
聽著，克拉蕾，我不相信它
Look, Clary, I don't believe it.

1348
02:01:58,331 --> 02:02:00,041
這似乎不是真的，不在我的心�
It doesn't feel like the truth, not in my heart.

1349
02:02:01,668 --> 02:02:04,754
我只是不懂如何去面對這個世界
I just don't know how to look at the world anymore.

1350
02:02:04,838 --> 02:02:07,632
我看不到街道，紅綠燈和車
I don't see streets and traffic lights and cars.

1351
02:02:07,715 --> 02:02:09,676
眼前只是邪靈和天使
I see demons and angels.

1352
02:02:10,635 --> 02:02:11,636
一切都變了
Everything's different.

1353
02:02:11,719 --> 02:02:13,513
世界還是一樣的
The world's the same.

1354
02:02:14,430 --> 02:02:16,724
你才是變了的那個
You're the one who's different.

1355
02:02:22,939 --> 02:02:24,566
你還記得霍奇說的嗎？
Don't you remember what Hodge said?

1356
02:02:24,649 --> 02:02:25,859
什麼？
What?

1357
02:02:25,942 --> 02:02:27,610
所以故事都是真的
All the stories are true.

1358
02:02:41,087 --> 02:02:43,658
感謝觀影
